<p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"> </p><p></p>
<p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">Greetings!</span></p><p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p></p>
<p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">My name is Teko Bailey, and I am working RREACH on the four-year project to follow up with those who attended the GProCongress in Bangkok in 2016 in
