<p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p></p>
<p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">Through our follow up efforts, we also aim to track the training of 100,000 pastors and the raising up an additional 20,000 pastoral trainers globally.
 You can read more at </span><a href="http://www.gprocommission.org/"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">www.GProCommission.org</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">.
</span></p><p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"> </p><p></p>
<p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">I know you are busy, but I wanted to reach out and touch base to see how we can be praying for you. Secondly, I wondered if there are any needs you have
